<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='398647' id='t-398647'>And that's what you have to do to prepare children for education and for school.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='403872' id='t-403872'>And I'm working at all the energy I have</span>
