</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='479077' id='t-479077'>I was privileged to have that kind of good start.</span>
