10:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='634227' id='t-634227'>But it begins with the gift of a good start.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='637577' id='t-637577'>If we don't give that gift to each and every one of our kids,</span>
