<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='674555' id='t-674555'>We worked like dogs down in the garment industry every single day.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='678730' id='t-678730'>We're not doing it so that you can stick something up your nose</span>
