11:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='701171' id='t-701171'>They had expectations for all of the cousins</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='703697' id='t-703697'>and the extended family of immigrants that lived in the South Bronx,</span>
